StmtSimple.StatementText: SELECT mode_transport.categorie_nom AS "Categorie", (SUM(mobpro_ind_1.distance_chemin_court * mobpro_ind_1.coef_pond)/SUM(mobpro_ind_1.coef_pond)) AS "Distance trajet domicile - travail (moyenne)" FROM mobpro_ind_1, mode_transport WHERE mobpro_ind_1.mode_trans=mode_transport.mode_id GROUP BY mode_transport.categorie_nom
